Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject as the terminal activity in process variants
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject that directly follows SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Number of SW-EIC Reject occurrences across all cases in the event log
Percentage of SW-EIC Reject relative to the total number of all activity executions in the log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed at least once
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject in variants that never include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all cases where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not happen

Name: Ratio of SW-EIC Reject to SW-EIC Accept in the entire event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of SW-EIC Reject events that occur without any prior reviewer agreement (i.e., no SW-Reviewer Agreed in the case trace)
Metric: Number of 'SW-EIC Reject' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not occur

Name: Percentage of cases ending in SW-EIC Reject where the manuscript underwent initial plagiarism screening (Plagiarism Originality Report Completed occurred)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Frequency of SW-EIC Reject in variants that include more than three reviewer assignment attempts (e.g., multiple SW-AE Assign Reviewers or SW-Reviewer Declined)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject that occurs within 30 days of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: the average of the function base <= 30 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-EIC Reject' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of SW-EIC Reject decisions preceded by SW-AE Recommendation overdue
Metric: Number of 'SW-EIC Reject' activities for cases where activity 'SW-AE Recommendation overdue' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject in cases that passed the checklist phase (i.e., SW-Checklist Completed occurred before SW-Awaiting AE Assignment)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-EIC Reject' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject out of all final editorial decisions (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Major Revision, SW-EIC Minor Revision, SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit)
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': activity == 'SW-EIC Reject'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity in ['SW-EIC Accept', 'SW-EIC Major Revision', 'SW-EIC Minor Revision', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit', 'SW-EIC Reject']"}"

Name: Percentage of SW-EIC Reject among all rejection-related outcomes (including SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit and Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist)
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': activity == 'SW-EIC Reject'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity in ['SW-EIC Reject', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit', 'Immediate Reject Decision from the Checklist']"}"
